snippet.title: Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising – Grimnir Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The tempestuous god of wind alights on the battlefield! Grimnir is the fourth new playable character joining the roster of Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising—launching on Nov 30, 2023!

Official Website - Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising (English)
https://rising.granbluefantasy.jp/en/

Official GBVS Series X Account (formerly Twitter)
https://twitter.com/gbvs_official
